/*
 * Function name: this_player
 * Description:   returns the current active living object, no matter if
 *                npc or interactive user. Notice that this_player is undefined
 *                within functions called by delay (call_out) and that the
 *                value is changed via set_this_player.
 * Returns:       object
 */

 This is no longer a function but a macro call within the global include file
 (/kernel/include/global.h)
